quran[83]{c,v,t}:
  36,1,"Ya, Sin."
  36,2,"Nditsuba khu Ikurani yamachesi."
  36,3,"Toto ewe oli mulala khubarumwa."
  36,4,"Owuli khunjila ingololofu."
  36,5,"Khuno nookhwishia khwa Nyasaye Owamani, Owobukoosia muno."
  36,6,"Mbu kho wikanyilisie abandu ba basamwana balekanyilisibwa tawe, mana nabo bali mubukoyani."
  36,7,"Obwatoto likhuwa liamala okhubura khubaanji mubo, mana shibasuubilanga tawe."
  36,8,"Toto efwe khwaboya mwikosi mwabu nemikoye okhuula khubinwanwa, mana emirwe chiabu chilisa hekulu."
  36,9,"Mana nikhura imbeli wabu eshikalilo khandi inyuma wabu eshikalilo, mana nikhufunikha tsimoni tsiabu mana shibalolanga tawe."
  36,10,"Ne ninashilala sa khubo, obekanyilisie nohomba obule okhubekanyilisia, shibalisuubila tawe."
  36,11,"Toto ewe wikanyilisinjia ulia uloondanga ametsulisio mana naria Omunji Wetsimbabaasi, khukefisile, kho muboolere koomwikhoyo keshileshelo nende omurungo omulayi."
  36,12,"Toto efwe khulamusinjia abafu, ne khuhandikanga kabakholanga nende kabalekha inyuma. Ne buli eshindu khwashibikha obulai muno mushitabu shinoosinjia."
  36,13,"Ne bakanile imbakha nobachelasilia Abandu bolukongo, olwa betselwa nende Abarumwa."
  36,14,"Olwa khwabarumila babili, nibabakatsula mana nikhubametela owakhataru. Nibaboola mbu: “Toto efwe khurumilwe khwinywe.”"
  36,15,"Nibaboola mbu: “Enywe mulisa Abandu shinga efwe, ne (Nyasaye) Omunji Wetsimbabaasi shiyeshiakhwo shiosishiosi tawe, ne enywe mukatinjia butswa.”"
  36,16,"Baboola mbu: “Nyasaye wefu Omulesi amanyile mbu efwe toto khurumilwe khwinywe."
  36,17,"Ne khubula elindi tawe halali okhusia khuli habulafu.”"
  36,18,"Baboola mbu: “Efwe toto khulolanga lisubiro khwinywe. Nimulalekhana ninafu tawe, toto khulabalasa amachina, ne toto mulanyoolwa nende eshinyasio eshikhongo okhurula khwifwe.”"
  36,19,"Baboola mbu: “Lisubiro lwenyu lili khwinywe. Khulwa sa mbu mwitsulisibwe? Halali enywe muli sa abandu babura eshichelo?”"
  36,20,"Mana omusatsa mulala niyetsa okhurula mumbeka wolukongo olo nayuukanga muno, naboola mbu: “Enywe abandu banje, loonde Abarumwa bano."
  36,21,"Loonde balia abalabasabanga omurungo tawe, nabo abeene nabalunjifu."
  36,22,"Ne khulwa shina ndalalaama ulia wanoonga tawe, ne ewuwe niwamulikalusibwa."
  36,23,"Koo, endiile abanyasaye bandi balali Ye tawe? Nyasaye Omunji wetsimbabaasi niyanyenyela amabii, okhusaba khwenyu shikhulaakhoonya shiosishiosi tawe, nohomba shibakhahabina tawe."
  36,24,"Toto mana esie endio emba endi mubukori bwa habulafu."
  36,25,"Toto esie esuubiile khu Nyasaye wenyu Omulesi, kho rechelesie.”"
  36,26,"Naboolelwa mbu: “Injila mumukunda kwomwikulu.” Naboola mbu: “Abayie abandu banje bamanyanga khwo."
  36,27,"Shingala Nyasaye wanje Omulesi yandesheele mana niyanda mubalia abahelesibwa oluyali.”"
  36,28,"Ne shikhweshiakhwo khubandu be imbeli wuwe omukanda kweliyie okhurula mwikulu, ne shikhwali beshia tawe."
  36,29,"Lwali butswa oluyoka lulala, lola, bali bamalile okhusuma."
  36,30,"""Abaane, ebeelelela abandu banje. Omurumwa yesiyesi shiyabetselanga tawe okhula bamubayile."""
  36,31,"Koo, shibalolangakhwo nemikanda chinga chakhwasishia imbeli wabu? Abo toto shibali babakalushila tawe."
  36,32,"Ne toto boosi balikhung’asibwa barerwe imbeli wefu."
  36,33,"Ne eshimanyisio khubo ni liloba [eliumu] liafwa, khulilamusinjia mana khuchesemwo imele yabaliitsanga."
  36,34,"Ne nikhukasiamwo emikunda chia tsitende nende tsizabibu, ne nikhukasiamwo tsisebele."
  36,35,"Kho balie khubiamo bie, nende aka emikhono chiabu chilakholele tawe. Koo, shibakhupanga orio tawe!"
  36,36,"Obutswenufu nibwa Nyasaye waloonga eshisatsa neshikhasi bioosi khubimelanga mwiloba, nende enywe abeene, nende ebiabalamanyile tawe."
  36,37,"Ne eshilo neshimanyisio shindi khubo, olwa khurusinjiamwo eshiteere, ne lola, baba mushiilima."
  36,38,"Ne eliuba lichendanga khushichelo shalio. Esho nisho eshichelo shia Nyasaye Owamaani, Omumanyi muno."
  36,39,"Ne Omwesi khwakurereraho ameshelo okhula kukalukhe kube shingala likhamari liumile."
  36,40,"Eliuba shiniliula khumwesi nohomba eshilo okhubura eshitere tawe, nabo bioosi bibotokhananga khutsinjila tsiabio."
  36,41,"Ne ni eshimanyisio khubo mbu efwe khwachinga olwibulo lwabu musafina yitsule."
  36,42,"Ne nikhubalonjela okhurula khufwani eyo ebiabaninangakhwo."
  36,43,"Ne nikhwenya, nikhubasishia mumatsi, ne abulaho ubakhoonya nohomba shibahabinwa tawe."
  36,44,"Halali tsimbabaasi tsirulanga khwifwe, nende omwikhoyo kwebise bititi."
  36,45,"Ne nibaboolelwa mbu: “Mwilinde ehale nende kali imbeli wenyu nende kali inyuma wenyu, khomunyoole okhubeelwa tsimbabaasi.”"
  36,46,"Ne sishiboolelanga eshimanyisio shiosishiosi mubimanyisio bia Nyasaye wabu Omulesi, halali shibabukulangamwo oluchendo tawe."
  36,47,"Ne nibaboolelwa mbu: “Hane khubilia bia Nyasaye abakabile"", Abakhayi baboolelenga Abasuubili mbu: “Koo, khulisie balia ba Nyasaye niyenya nabalisia? Toto enywe muli mubukori bwa habulafu.”"
  36,48,"Ne baboolanga mbu: “Kamukhulakanga kano kalirulila lina, nimuli toto abahabwene?”"
  36,49,"Shibalindanga halali oluyoka lulala butswa lulibabukula nabo nibali mukhusolana."
  36,50,"Mana shibalinyoola okhulaamila nohomba shibalikalukha khubandu babu tawe."
  36,51,"Na olwa olwika lulifurwamwo, balirula mubilindwa nibelushila ewa Nyasaye wabu Omulesi."
  36,52,"Baliboola mbu: “Abayie! Wina ukhulamusiyie okhurula wakhubeele nikhukonele. Kano niko aka Omunji wetsimbabaasi yalaka, ne Abarumwa nibaboola katoto.”"
  36,53,"Ne shiluliba halali oluyoka lulala butswa, ne lola, boosi balikhung’asibwa imbeli wefu."
  36,54,"Mana olwa lelo abulaho yesiyesi ulikholelwa amabii kosikosi, ne shimulirungwa halali kalia kamwakholanga."
  36,55,"Toto abandu ba mumukunda kwomwikulu lelo bali khumilimo khubusangafu."
  36,56,"Bo nende abakhaye babu nibali mubinikha bayeshele khubisaala biobwokholo."
  36,57,"Balinyolamwo tsimbia tsioosi tsiebiamo, ne balinyoolamwo buli eshiabeenya."
  36,58,"“Omulembe” nilikhuwa lilirula khu Nyasaye Omulesi, Wobukoosia muno."
  36,59,"Ne enywe abetsimbii mwiyawule olwalelo."
  36,60,"Koo, shindalakana ninanyu enywe Abandu mbu mulalaama Shetani tawe? Toto ye ni Omusuku wenyu owa habulafu."
  36,61,"Ni mbu munaame esie. Ino niyo injila ingololofu."
  36,62,"Ne khubwatoto ye yakosia omukanda omukhongo mwinywe, koo shimwekhonyerangakhwo obwongo tawe?"
  36,63,"Mana ino niyo Jahanam yamwalakungwa."
  36,64,"Injilemwo lelo shingala mwakhayanga."
  36,65,"Olwa lelo khulatimbia eminwa chiabu, ne emikhono chiabu chilaboola ninafu, ne ebilenje biabu bilarusia obuloli khu kalia kabakholanga."
  36,66,"Ne khwenyanga, khwakhatimbiyie tsimoni tsiabu baba nibashilanila injila halali bakhalutsi barie?"
  36,67,"Ne khwenyanga, khwakhabakalukhaniye ifwani nibali hao butswa, mana shibakhanyalile okhutsia nohomba okhukalukha tawe."
  36,68,"Ne wakhukofusia, khumukalusinjia inyuma mubulonji, mana koo, shibeekhonyerangakhwo obwongo tawe?"
  36,69,"Ne shikhwamwechesia [Muhammad] amashairi tawe, ne elo shilienyekhana khuye tawe. Shino ni eshitsulisio nende Ikurani iretsanga abulafu."
  36,70,"Kho shikanyilisilie ushili omulamu, ne likhuwa libure khubakhayi."
  36,71,"Koo, shibalolangakhwo mbu khwabaloonjela okhurulana khumilimo chia emikhono chiefu tsisolo tsiemiruko, etsia barukanga."
  36,72,"Ne nikhubanguyisilia etsindi mutsisolo etso tsiabaninangakhwo, ne etsindi batsiliitsaanga."
  36,73,"Ne bo banyoolanga mutsisolo etso akobukhonyi nende ebinywebwa, kho mana shibakhupanga orio tawe?"
  36,74,"Ne batila abanyasaye bandi habundu wa Nyasaye mbu khobanyoole obukhoonyi."
  36,75,"Shibalinyala okhubakhonya tawe halali abo nibo baliba abasikari babu olwa balikhwitsila."
  36,76,"Mana amakhuwa kabu kalakhubelesia tawe. Toto efwe khwamanya kabafisanga nende kabaretsaanga habulafu."
  36,77,"Ne omundu shalolanga ta mbu khwamuloonga okhurulana nende indonyande ya amatsi kolwibulo, ne lola awosa, naaba omuseeri wa habulafu."
  36,78,"Ne nakhuchelasilia, naye yebilila okhulongwa khukhwe. Mana naboola mbu: “Ni wina oyo ulilamusia ebikumba nibimalile okhubulungukha?”"
  36,79,"Boola mbu: “Alibilamusia ulia wabiloonga olwokhuranjilila, naye ni Omumanyi muno wabuli okhuloonga khwoosi."
  36,80,"Ulia wabakholela okhunyoola omulilo okhurula khumusala omubisi, mana nimunyoola okhubwana omulilo okhurulana ninakwo."""
  36,81,"Koo, waloonga likulu nende eshialo shanyala okhulonga bafwana ninabo tawe? Khulwa shina, naye niye Omuloonji Omukhongo, Omumanyi muno?"
  36,82,"Toto likhuwa lilie niyenya eshindu, ashiboolela butswa mbu: “Ba!” Ni shiba."
  36,83,"Mana yatswenukha ulia wobwami bwa buli eshindu buli mumukhono kukwe, ne ewuwe niwo wamulikalusibwa."
